creator: Telco Quest
descriptionHtml:
What do we offer here:
We are offering you to assume a role of the interceptor pilot serving on the "legendary" Centaurian carrier "Gerald" where you will be playing a key role in the war for independence between Cantauri colony and all mighty and prosperous but corrupted "Alliance", defending all what "Alliance" stood for before the ruling power was taken by the "Cult".

You will be assigned on the different missions such as:

- Escort friendly transports
- Retrieve object
- Eliminate enemy transport
- Stay in the "shadow" of the spy boat, at the same time protecting it
- And others such as duel, seek and destroy, etc...

This app do not contain in app ads, however after first two missions we will ask you to donate small amount to unlock the rest of the game.
descriptionShort: Become a legend of the Centaurian war for independence

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Corrected bug on the mission 4 target assignment
Corrected multiple typos

title: Gerald - war chronicles

creator: Telco Quest
descriptionHtml:
What do we offer here:

We are offering you to assume a role of the interceptor pilot serving on the "legendary" Centaurian carrier "Gerald", where you will be playing a key role in the war for independence between Cantaurian colony and all mighty and prosperous but corrupted "Alliance", defending all what "Alliance" stood for before the ruling power was taken by the "Cult".

You will be assigned on the different missions such as:

- Escort friendly transports
- Retrieve object
- Eliminate enemy transport
- Stay in the "shadow" of the spy boat, at the same time protecting it
- And others such as duel, seek and destroy, etc...

For each mission you will have to choose your strategy wisely. Sometimes it is wise to estimate the trajectory of the escorted object and pull whatever is expecting it ahead on you in some other occasions you might wait for the backup before engaging the enemy. And at all times use your ship ability to move backwards and the speed boost.

If you have any suggestions or have any questions, do not hesitate to express it via e-mail contac@telcoquest.com
descriptionShort: Become a legend of Centaurian war for independence

Updated textures and multiple user interface ellements
